notes: This file is served at /facebook-golden-templates.json and used by the extension as a fallback when local recordings are missing.
Populate it by running ProfitOrbitExtension.downloadFacebookGoldenTemplates() in the profitorbit.io console (with the extension installed), then committing the downloaded JSON here.
Tokens (fb_dtsg/lsd/jazoest) and user IDs are refreshed at runtime; do not store cookies here.
